title: Weis Hickman Core Dragonlance AudioBook Collection
description:
A Collection of the Core Dragonlance Novels by Original Authors/Creators 
Margaret Weis and Tracy Hickman

Included Audio Books:
Chronicles-
Dragons of Autumn Twilight
Dragons of Winter Night
Dragons of Spring Dawning
Dragons of Summer Flame

Legends-
Time of the Twins
War of the Twins
Test of the Twins

Raistlin Chronicles-
The Soulforge

The Lost Chronicles-
Dragons of the Dwarven Depths
Dragons of the Highlord Skies
Dragons of the Hourglass Mage

War of Souls-
Dragons of a Fallen Sun
Dragons of a Lost Star
Dragons of a Vanished Moon

Each Book is in a seperate .zip file
Readme File with Listening Order included


File Quality varies between books, as this collection has been compiled from multiple sources. The majority of the recordings are unabridged, but a few of them are not.
